data.description: Located on a generous lot in the desirable neighborhood of Idlewilde, this home still contains a lot of its original charm like built-ins, ample kitchen storage space, custom window treatments and more. Backyard features custom touches like a bridge, stonework, and paved walkways. Bring your creative ideas because this home is ready for a new owner.
